String class: designed to store symblos(letters, numbers, specical characters
in z form of a group. There are many methods already written by java dev. that we can just use.
This is the most widely  used class in java.For example
    length()
    startsWith()
    endsWith()
    contains()= checks if contains a specific word, letter
Why we should learn about this class.
    1. very important for coding question
    2. most widely used class in all java
    3. most of the info in real life is present in the form of string.

note: very important for coding questions for the interview;
    1. if else
    2. loops
    3. arrays
    4. Strings